<h3>Booking</h3>

-Can be booked Monday thru Thursday 4pm to 1 am

-Friday thru Sunday, 2 pm to 2 am


Bookings can only be done once a user creates an account, and it is here that they can
store their personal information, such as credit card number, and contant information, and
as well view and edit their bookings. Once logged in, the user can view a calender of 
available bookings, from which they can choose a room to book, or see which rooms they've
booked.

Cancellations:

Cancellations that are made 4 hours before the a scheduled appointment will prevent the
user from booking another room for 12 hours.
